OL,3,CTrain safety failure identified as
OL,4,Cfactor in fatal train crash
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FAn automated system which helps train
OL,8,Fwheels grip tracks failed on a train
OL,9,Finvolved in a fatal crash in mid-Wales
OL,10,Fon October 21, investigators said.
OL,12,FHoses fitted to the Transport for
OL,13,FWales (TfW) train to discharge sand
OL,14,Fwhen wheels slide during braking were
OL,15,F"blocked", the Rail Accident
OL,16,FInvestigation Branch (RAIB) said.
OL,18,FTfW and Network Rail said it is
OL,19,F"fundamental that we await the
OL,20,Ffindings of the full report".
