OL,7,FThe train was travelling at between
OL,8,F15mph and 24mph when it collided head-
OL,9,Fon with another TfW train travelling
OL,10,Fat around 6mph.
OL,12,FPassenger David Tudor Evans, 66, died
OL,13,Fand four other people were seriously
OL,14,Fhurt.
OL,16,FA further 11 people suffered injuries
OL,17,Fwhich required hospital treatment.
OL,19,FBoth trains involved in the crash were
OL,20,Ftwo-carriage class 158 units.
