OL,7,FThe train with the failed sanding
OL,8,Fsystem was travelling west to
OL,9,FAberystwyth.
OL,11,FIt was supposed to stop inside a loop
OL,12,Fto allow an eastbound train to pass on
OL,13,Fthe single track.
OL,15,FInitial analysis of the on-board data
OL,16,Frecorder shows the driver applied the
OL,17,Fbrakes as the train neared the loop,
OL,18,Fduring which time the wheels began to
OL,19,Fslide.
