OL,7,FAround 40 seconds later, the driver
OL,8,Fmade an emergency brake demand, which
OL,9,Fremained in place until the crash.
OL,11,FThe train passed through the loop and
OL,12,Frejoined the single line, sliding for
OL,13,Faround 900 metres downhill before the
OL,14,Fcollision occurred.
OL,16,FThe RAIB said its investigation will
OL,17,Fconsider several aspects, such as the
OL,18,Fsanding system, the performance of the
OL,19,Ftrains, and the policies of TfW and
OL,20,FNetwork Rail related to managing the
OL,21,Frisk of wheels sliding.
