OL,7,FA joint statement from Transport for
OL,8,FWales and Network Rail said:
OL,9,F"Following the rail collision in Powys
OL,10,Fon Monday 21 October 2024, Transport
OL,11,Ffor Wales and Network Rail have fully
OL,12,Fcooperated with the British Transport
OL,13,FPolice, Office of Rail and Road and
OL,14,Fthe Rail Accident Investigation Branch.
OL,16,F"As investigations are currently still
OL,17,Fongoing, we'll continue to work
OL,18,Ftogether with investigators to
OL,19,Funderstand what happened and await the
OL,20,Ffull conclusion and recommendations of
OL,21,Fthe investigation.
