OL,7,F"Safety is always our main priority
OL,8,Ffor our customers and colleagues, and
OL,9,Fwe have carried out enhanced checks to
OL,10,Fthe trains and the railway line to
OL,11,Fenable the reopening of the Cambrian
OL,12,Fline on Monday 28 October 2024.
OL,14,F"At this early stage of the
OL,15,Finvestigation, it's fundamental that
OL,16,Fwe await the findings of the full
OL,17,Freport and show sensitivity towards
OL,18,Four customers, colleagues, the local
OL,19,Fcommunity and the families of those
OL,20,Faffected by the incident."
