OL,7,FA close family friend of Mr Evans, who
OL,8,Fdid not want to be named, told news
OL,9,Fagency PA: "The report is quite clear
OL,10,Fthat there have been failings with the
OL,11,Fsystems.
OL,13,F"It's of great concern that this
OL,14,Fshould have happened.
OL,16,F"In light of this initial disclosure I
OL,17,Fwould call for a totally independent
OL,18,Finquiry, possibly a public inquiry,
OL,19,Fthat looks at all the aspects of the
OL,20,Finvestigation and what went wrong."
